{
  "stem": "13524.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Interest in living.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He could not work anymore because he couldn't walk.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the moment he was falling over, he was beaten.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the fact that they have taken my father-- my mother away, my father and myself were completely destroyed.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Father lost interest in living, and I was, without speaking to him, convinced that Mother went to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was terrible blow to both of us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] We did know a doctor in this-- there was a sort of hospital, a place where one would go when one had some injury.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "His name was Dr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Lefkowitch, whom we knew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because when we were in the ghetto, we lived in the same house.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know, each time the transport went away, the ghetto was made smaller.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And on the second occasion, we lived in the house with a family called [INAUDIBLE], to whose son my sister was really engaged.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And next door, Dr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Lefkowitch used to live.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And Mrs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Gross, whose husband also was a doctor-- that famous Dr.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Gross, from Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So I went and I begged they should take my father to hospital to give him chance to recuperate, to revive him.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] It was no revival.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They have taken him to hospital, to isolation hospital.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And the following morning when I came from night duty, I wanted to see my father and I brought him a little cup with boiled potatoes.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Nobody wanted to come to the gate to pick the potatoes from me to take to my father.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And you know, you're sort of intuitive, really.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You realize something is not quite right.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Eventually I stood there and waited and waited.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
